<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Under Maintenance | Vamper</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f8fc 0%, #e9f2ff 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .maintenance-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.08);
            padding: 3rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .icon-wrapper {
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            max-width: 250px;
        }
        .icon-wrapper img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }
        .brand-logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #0d6efd;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="maintenance-card">
        <div class="brand-logo">
            <i class="bi bi-code-slash"></i> Vamper
        </div>
        
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <img src="https://cdni.iconscout.com/illustration/premium/thumb/website-maintenance-illustration-download-in-svg-png-gif-file-formats--under-construction-page-error-service-pack-network-communication-illustrations-6430752.png" alt="Maintenance Robot">
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">We're upgrading Vamper!</h2>
        
        <p class="text-muted mb-4" style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Sorry for the inconvenience but we're performing some maintenance at the moment. 
            We'll be back online shortly!
        </p>

        <div class="bg-light rounded-3 p-3 text-start d-inline-block text-muted small">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i> If you need immediate assistance, please contact us at <a href="mailto:buithanhliem14022002@gmail.com" class="text-decoration-none">buithanhliem14022002@gmail.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>